name: Become a Technical Speaker
description: There are a lot of people in the community who are amazing developers. I realized some of them never share or speak at a public event. This is mostly for them. The devs I love the most and the developers who are highly knowledgable but too shy to share.

name: Introduction to Bluetooth Low Energy
description: Next up, TECH TALK TUESDAYS is proud to have Kheng Meng share with us on Bluetooth Low Energy - a new and emerging wireless communication standard designed primarily to save power and was only ratified in 2010. Join us for his presentation titled Introduction to Bluetooth Low Energy, where he will be showing how to harness this new technology for your hardware projects with live demos and coding examples involving the Arduino, Raspberry Pi, Android and iOS.
location: The Prototyping Lab @ NDC - 111 Middle Rd, #01-02 National Design Centre 188969 SG
